{"tid":1028090,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本 PlayStation Vita 主機將於近日停止供貨 宣告 PlayStation 掌上型主機業務的終結","createTime":"2019-02-19T09:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T09:54:21.000Z","uid":85180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"37217a6dbad1d848e7bc16e145ef02a35786ba8a","tid":1028090,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"日本 PlayStation Vita 主機將於近日停止供貨 宣告 PlayStation 掌上型主機業務的終結<br />\n（GNN 記者 Sam 報導） 2019-02-19 12:16:37<br />\n根據 PlayStation 日本官方網站的產品頁面訊息，目前僅有 2 款仍在販售中的 PlayStation Vita 掌上型主機「PlayStation Vita Wi-Fi 型號 黑」與「PlayStation Vita Wi-Fi 型號 水波藍」將於近日停止供貨，且目前並無後繼款式的消息，表示推出至今 7 年多的這款掌上型主機將走入歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/25/1e55f606c3c4f75c81d894597d140j15.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F25%2F1e55f606c3c4f75c81d894597d140j15.JPG&h=9c188f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPlayStation Vita 是索尼互動娛樂於 2011 年 1 月發表的旗下第 2 代掌上型主機，承襲前代 PlayStation Portable 的造型設計與理念，以高效能整合處理器與細緻的 OLED 顯示螢幕提供當時最高等級的 3D 繪圖影音效果，並導入家用主機主流的雙類比搖桿以及獨特的雙面觸碰輸入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/14/0000467214.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F14%2F0000467214.JPG&h=888f567e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2011 年 1 月時任索尼電腦娛樂（SCE，後更名為索尼互動娛樂 SIE）總裁兼執行長的平井一夫正式發表代號「NGP」的 PSP 後繼機種，後定名為「PlayStation Vita」<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/84/0000543884.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F84%2F0000543884.JPG&h=4ac6a980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2011 年推出的 PCH-1000 系列 PS Vita，採用鮮豔高對比的 OLED 顯示螢幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/66/0000865766.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F66%2F0000865766.JPG&h=922e014c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPS Vita 於 2011 年底起陸續在日本、亞洲與歐美地區推出，雖然具備硬體優勢，但競爭產品 Nintendo 3DS 搶先於當年 3 月推出，且 8 月就閃電降價 1 萬日圓提振買氣。加上 9 月又宣布原本左右 PSP 買氣的《魔物獵人》系列新作將移籍到 N3DS 上推出，使得 PS Vita 未能繼承 PSP 的市場版圖。雖然後續在 SIE 主導下推出了多款性質類似的 &ldquo;共鬥&rdquo; 遊戲，但皆未能扭轉局勢。"},{"pid":"293619cf33227b283284aee85048ae82c388130b","tid":1028090,"uid":215441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"如果佢行micro SD可能冇死得咁快"},{"pid":"305b0892305c24a7400ad75896a82d9f6c859ac8","tid":1028090,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"仲等緊隻mhp3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09f02665b41a55eed339660d8c6e6056a281001","tid":1028090,"uid":92376,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"305b0892305c24a7400ad75896a82d9f6c859ac8","tid":1028090,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"仲等緊隻mhp3G<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://zt.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/scbd/2012/1/201201271203547763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzt.tgbus.com%2FUploadFiles%2Fscbd%2F2012%2F1%2F201201271203547763.jpg&h=6e41704f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030195e88fea7c28576b35b6606f6927b8cf4150","tid":1028090,"uid":72142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"又瀨落capcoin到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc06e5659e5512a7e552a1f2fda4209e9cdc68","tid":1028090,"uid":1256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"有無人會用呢部野remote play PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />